From 01db770aa8233a60f4bcc35434ebf912123f5eda Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vivek Chettri <vchettri@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 2 Jul 2025 21:31:16 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] QSDK: CP: wifi: ath12k: Add wrapper APIs for service
 class configuration

Add support to define service classes which is a set of QoS profiles.

The services classes is defined on top of existing QoS profiles.
A service class will contain either downlink or uplink QoS  profiles or
both Downlink and Uplink QoS profiles.

Add support for the following APIs
	ath12k_sdwf_map_service_class
		API to map service class to Uplink and Downlink QoS profiles.
	ath12k_sdwf_unmap_service_class
		API to umap service class to Uplink and Downlink QoS profiles.
	ath12k_sdwf_get_dl_qos_id
		API to fetch the DL QoS profiles from a service class.
	ath12k_sdwf_get_ul_qos_id
		API to fetch the UL QoS profiles from a service class.
	ath12k_sdwf_service_configured
		API to check if service class configured.

Signed-off-by: Vivek Chettri <vchettri@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
